It implies that good swimming athletes coming from <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">five</ENAMEX> continents and <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</ENAMEX> oceans assembled together in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Rome</ENAMEX> to strengthen understanding and enhance friendship through competition .
